.TH "nvme_scan_ctrl" 9 "nvme_scan_ctrl" "July 2025" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_scan_ctrl \- Scan on a controller
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "nvme_ctrl_t" nvme_scan_ctrl
.BI "(nvme_root_t r "  ","
.BI "const char *name "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "r" 12
nvme_root_t object
.IP "name" 12
Name of the controller
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Scans a controller with sysfs name \fIname\fP and add it to \fIr\fP.
.SH "RETURN"
nvme_ctrl_t object
